               stealing, on the <rs id="t18321018-239-cd1350" type="crimeDate">26th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18321018-239-off1349 t18321018-239-cd1350"></join>, 1 piece of iron, called a poppet-head, value 13s.; 1 collar and mandle, value 13s.; 2 rest-screws, value 10s.; 2 tops and boxes, value 5s., and 1 iron cramp, value 12s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18321018-239-victim2079" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     Bradick
                  <interp inst="t18321018-239-victim2079" type="surname" value="Bradick"></interp>
